data.description: **Back on Market through no fault of Seller's** Welcome to your dream Craftsman home! This custom-built beauty is nestled on a sprawling 1.6-acre lot, offering the perfect blend of luxury and tranquility. With 3 spacious bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, this home boasts a warm and inviting atmosphere. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the centerpiece of the living room - a stunning stacked stone fireplace that exudes rustic charm. The oversized breakfast area is perfect for morning gatherings or casual dining, and the Heart Pine Plank floors throughout the home add a touch of timeless elegance. This residence is not just beautiful but also practical, with a brand-new roof installed in August 2023 for peace of mind. The kitchen features solid surface countertops, making meal prep a breeze. Outside, you'll find a rocking chair porch, the ideal spot to unwind and take in the scenic beauty of your expansive property. In addition to a huge 2-car detached garage, there's an ample parking pad for your convenience. Don't miss out on this unique opportunity to own a piece of craftsmanship on 1.6 acres of land. Schedule a showing today and make this remarkable home yours!
